title: IHC declares NA-35, 36 demarcation null and void
content:
ISLAMABAD, Dec 15 (APP): The Islamabad High Court (IHC) has declared the demarcation of the two National Assembly seats, NA-35 and NA-36, null and void.
The Chief Justice of IHC, Amir Farooq issued the order on Friday.
The court directed the Election Commission of Pakistan (ECP) to redefine the constituencies after hearing all the parties again.
